snippet.title: Quake | Mock Trailer (2010)
snippet.description:
Next in the line of Mock trailers. Quake, the succesor to DOOM. This badass of Polygonal Power sent an aftershock through the industry in 1996. 

It's three major features were improved netplay/deathmatch, fully 3D polygonal graphics, and a soundtrack by Trent "Nine Inch Nails" Reznor. 

The soundtrack for the trailer is a custom mix of the first track on the Quake CD, mixed and cut by Open Maw Productions. Original track by Trent Reznor.

It's chief compeition  came from a certain alien ass kicker.

Part of a bigger project in progress. A series of trailers based around older content. The concept being to create trailers for games that never really had them.

Website:
http://openmaw.x10hosting.com/index.htm
